data.description: Welcome to this upscale, immaculate home!  From the moment you walk in, you'll see the high-end finishes.  The main level offers an elegant open concept living area  complete with a gorgeous fireplace.  Entertaining is easy with the seamless access to the kitchen and dining area.  The master suite is spacious and inviting -- offering his and hers vanities, an oversized walk-in shower and extra large master closet.  Upstairs, this modified Ashley Home floorplan provides an additional area that can become whatever you want -- a media room, family room, office, etc.  You'll also find three large bedrooms as well as two more full baths.  There's an abundance of space throughout the home.  Outside, you can relax on the front porch area and greet neighbors passing by on the sidewalks provided throughout the subdivision.  Looking to chill out after work?  Your back yard is fully enclosed with a new 6' privacy fence.   Enjoy grilling out on the patio while the children and/or pets play.  In addition, the community offers a new pool, cabana, and playground to enjoy.  Magnolia Station is located in the highly sought after Lula area and offers easy access to Ga 365.  Head south towards Gainesville/metro Atlanta or go north and plan a day or weekend trip to experience some of the beauty and attractions in Northeast Georgia.   Don't wait -- call to schedule your tour of this home today!
